20:39.538 --> 20:44.410 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Shortly after
Betsy DeVos'
confirmation hearing began this
evening, she

20:44.443 --> 20:49.815 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
