to push for
expanded school choice around
the country,

20:49.849 --> 20:54.186 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
much as she did during her two
decades as
a major political force in her
home state

20:54.220 --> 20:55.988 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of Michigan.

20:56.021 --> 20:57.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BETSY DEVOS, Education Secretary
Nominee:
Parents no longer believe that a
one-size-fits-all

20:57.923 --> 21:01.694 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
model of learning meets the
needs -- need
of every child.

21:01.727 --> 21:08.167 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
