exist, whether
magnet, virtual, charter, home,
faith-based,

21:08.200 --> 21:10.102 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
or any combination.

21:10.136 --> 21:14.507 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Yet, too many parents are denied
access to
the full range of options.

21:14.540 --> 21:18.677 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: DeVos has
neither taught,
nor worked as an educator or
supervisor in

21:18.711 --> 21:24.550 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a school system, but she and her
family, whose
net worth tops $5 billion, have
used that

21:24.583 --> 21:30.756 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
wealth and influence as
advocates and political
donors to create more charter
schools in Michigan,

21:30.789 --> 21:33.726 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and to try legalizing school
vouchers.

21:33.759 --> 21:37.696 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
