public money on
private or parochial schools.

21:37.730 --> 21:42.001 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She lost the voucher battle in
Michigan, but
still champions their use.

21:42.034 --> 21:45.971 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Democrats are worried that DeVos
will undermine
public education across the
country.

21:46.005 --> 21:47.773 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

21:47.806 --> 21:51.076 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PATTY MURRAY (D), Washington: We
focus our
federal policies and investments
on strengthening

21:51.110 --> 21:57.049 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
public schools for all students,
and certainly
not towards diverting taxpayer
dollars to

21:57.082 --> 22:01.620 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
fund vouchers that don't work
for unaccountable
private schools.

22:01.654 --> 22:07.393 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I have major concerns with how
you spent your
career and fortune fighting to
privatize public

22:07.426 --> 22:10.629 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
education and gut investments in
public schools.

22:10.663 --> 22:15.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: DeVos'
philosophy fits right
in with president-elect Trump's,
who pledged

22:15.034 --> 22:20.472 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
during the campaign to provide
$20 billion
in federal support for charter
schools and

22:20.506 --> 22:22.374 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
vouchers.

22:22.408 --> 22:25.945 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Her support for charters, which
are publicly
funded schools, but which
operate independently,

22:25.978 --> 22:28.280 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
is the subject of particular
scrutiny.

22:28.314 --> 22:33.052 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Detroit Free Press found
that 75 percent
of schools in Michigan performed
better than

22:33.085 --> 22:37.756 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
