civil rights,
college affordability and
for-profit colleges.

23:08.320 --> 23:12.491 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For more on Betsy DeVos and what
she means
for education in America, I'm
joined by two

23:12.524 --> 23:14.994 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
