34:27.098 --> 34:30.402 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: He was holed up at
home and
reeling from untreated HIV that
had progressed

34:30.435 --> 34:32.037 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
