young son, and
cycled through Houston's
hospitals.

34:34.973 --> 34:39.811 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAYNA GURLEY: When we first met
Timmy, he
was very hard to engage.

34:39.844 --> 34:46.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
