lights turned
back on.

34:54.292 --> 35:03.001 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Now Williams' HIV is
undetectable and his
health, and life, have been
steadied.

35:03.034 --> 35:07.072 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Although these efforts involve
many staff
members, in the two years since
the Patient

35:07.105 --> 35:11.643 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Care Intervention Center has
been up and running,
costs for those in the program
have gone down

35:11.676 --> 35:15.180 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
83 percent and hospital visits
by 70 percent.

35:15.213 --> 35:19.851 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAYNA GURLEY: I really want to
get to know
them and spend time with them.

35:19.884 --> 35:22.821 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: But it can be
difficult to keep
these programs moving.

35:22.854 --> 35:27.359 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Often, those savings go straight
to insurance
companies and government payers.

35:27.392 --> 35:31.529 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And Dr. Buck and Dayna Gurley
were once banned
from a Houston hospital that was
afraid of

35:31.563 --> 35:34.599 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
