of our health
care system, what are we trying
to accomplish?

36:12.804 --> 36:18.510 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: But Brenner still
believes these
intensive efforts are the best
way to help

36:18.543 --> 36:20.545 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
