36:20.578 --> 36:24.015 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He's now healthy enough to make
his way around
the city on his own.

36:24.049 --> 36:27.185 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He says Gurley did more than
rescue him from
his darkest days.

36:27.218 --> 36:33.425 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TIMMY WILLIAMS: I had to put it
