that no one is going to do it
for me.

36:33.458 --> 36:34.426 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I have to do it for myself.

36:34.459 --> 36:36.094 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I have got to step out and do it
myself.

36:36.127 --> 36:37.228 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Read this here.

36:37.262 --> 36:38.763 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
STUDENT: This whole thing?

36:38.797 --> 36:40.565 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
TIMMY WILLIAMS: Yes.

36:40.598 --> 36:44.569 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: At home now with
his son, his
illness no longer gets in the
way of being

36:44.602 --> 36:47.072 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
