38:07.919 --> 38:13.224 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Longtime friend
and senior
White House adviser Valerie
Jarrett says his

38:13.258 --> 38:17.662 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
